      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my pride and joy, and I've made sure every inch is spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
