    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage since the day it left the showroom. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found across the body. Inside, the cabin retains that distinct 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats from day one. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound system, functions with surgical precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It drives with the same tightness and smoothness as it did the day it was manufactured. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that has been meticulously curated by a single enthusiast owner. Full documentation and service records are available for review.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
